::Fractyl::

Fractyl shrugs, limping toward the shuttle. "Why in the pit not? I can hold out there for a slagging while until I can contact my faction."

He reaches the shuttle and starts climbing up the hatch, having a bit of trouble with it.

> ::VorbIss::
> 
> "Well then," replied VorbIss, "I'm sorry I overestimated you." VorbIss 
> smirked. "This shuttle is owned by a faction called The Alliance, who wanted 
> me to join them. I am, I expect, about to leave in it to meet them. They may 
> well help you as well."
